title: Jets, Mets, Rangers all home for 1st time since 1999
text: > Top News Jets, Mets, Rangers all home for 1st time since 1999 FILE - In this Sept. 27, 2015, file photo, New York Jets wide receiver Brandon Marshall (15) makes a touchdown catch as Philadelphia Eagles free safety Malcolm Jenkins defends during an NFL football game in East Rutherford, N.J. Virtually every team relies on at least one receiver who is taller than 6-1, with some owning a collection of them. Marshall goes 6-4 and sidekick Eric Decker is 6-3. (AP Photo/Bill Kostroun, File)
